    "custom_liquid_AyeTjK": {
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "{% assign lang = localization.language.iso_code | downcase %}lang:{{lang}}\n<div class=\"page-width\" id=\"faq\">\n  <h2 class=\"faq-title\">\n    {% if lang == 'en' %}Frequently Asked Questions{%- else -%}よくある質問{% endif %}\n  </h2>\n  <div class=\"faq-container\">\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"faq-question\">\n        <div class=\"faq-question-text\">\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">Q</span>\n          {% if lang == 'en' %}When will the serial number plate for the pre-order bonus be finalized?{%- else -%}先行予約特典のシリアルナンバープレートの番号は、いつ確定しますか？{% endif %}\n        </div>\n        <svg class=\"toggle-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 36 36\">\n          <path class=\"bar-horizontal\" d=\"M9 18.5h18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n          <path class=\"bar-vertical\" d=\"M18.5 9v18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </a>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">A：</span>\n        {% if lang == 'en' %}We will notify you of your reserved serial number at the time we receive your reservation application.<br>\n        ※ If you cancel after reserving, the assigned number will be lost and passed on to the next applicant.<br>\n        ※ Even if you re-apply, earlier numbers will not be reassigned. If at that time the 100 pre-order limit has been exceeded, you will not be eligible for the bonus.<br>\n        ※ Only if a customer with a younger serial number cancels, your number may move up. Please note that the number you ultimately receive may differ from the initial notice, but it will never be a later number.<br>\n        ※ The finalized number will be confirmed in the shipping notice sent after payment (after Oct 14).{%- else -%}\n        予約申込書を弊社が受領した時点で取得予定のシリアルナンバーを事前通知させていただきます。<br>\n        ※予約後にキャンセルされた場合には、取得したシリアルナンバーは消失し、次順のご予約者様に繰り上げられます。<br>\n        ※再度ご予約された場合でも、若い番号は戻りません。また、再度ご予約された時点で、100脚の先行数を超えていた場合、先行特典を受けることができませんのでご注意ください。<br>\n        ※より若いシリアルナンバーを取得予定の購入希望者様によるキャンセルが発生した場合のみ、シリアルナンバーの繰上げが発生します。お手元に届く製品のシリアルナンバーが予約時に通知したものと変更になる場合がありますが、予約時に通知した番号より後ろの番号になる事はありません。<br>\n        ※10/14以降の入金後の発送前連絡にて、確定したシリアルナンバーを通知させていただきます。{% endif %}\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"faq-question\">\n        <div class=\"faq-question-text\">\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">Q</span>\n          {% if lang == 'en' %}Was this actually exhibited in the Japan Pavilion?{%- else -%}日本館で実際に展示されていたものですか？{% endif %}\n        </div>\n        <svg class=\"toggle-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 36 36\">\n          <path class=\"bar-horizontal\" d=\"M9 18.5h18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n          <path class=\"bar-vertical\" d=\"M18.5 9v18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </a>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">A：</span>\n        {% if lang == 'en' %}No, it was not actually exhibited. The differences are as follows:<br>\n        <Stool><br>\n        ・No Japan Pavilion logo<br>\n        ・Some specifications differ<br>\n        <Miniature><br>\n        ・Not exhibited in the Pavilion<br>\n        ・Color slightly different, no disassembly structure{%- else -%}\n        日本館で実際に展示されていたものではありません。具体的な違いは以下の通りです。<br>\n        <スツール><br>\n        ・日本館のロゴはありません<br>\n        ・一部仕様が異なります<br>\n        <ミニチュア><br>\n        ・日本館に展示しておりません<br>\n        ・色合いが少し異なり、分解構造は採用しておりません{% endif %}\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"faq-question\">\n        <div class=\"faq-question-text\">\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">Q</span>\n          {% if lang == 'en' %}Does filling out the reservation form count as a reservation?{%- else -%}予約フォーム記入で予約とみなされますか？{% endif %}\n        </div>\n        <svg class=\"toggle-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 36 36\">\n          <path class=\"bar-horizontal\" d=\"M9 18.5h18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n          <path class=\"bar-vertical\" d=\"M18.5 9v18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </a>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">A：</span>\n        {% if lang == 'en' %}No. Your reservation is confirmed once you submit the form and receive a confirmation email.{%- else -%}ご予約フォーム（製品購入申込）を入力し送信していただき、申込受付完了メールの案内をもって予約完了となります。{% endif %}\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"faq-question\">\n        <div class=\"faq-question-text\">\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">Q</span>\n          {% if lang == 'en' %}When is payment due for the reserved product?{%- else -%}予約商品の支払いはいつ頃ですか？{% endif %}\n        </div>\n        <svg class=\"toggle-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 36 36\">\n          <path class=\"bar-horizontal\" d=\"M9 18.5h18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n          <path class=\"bar-vertical\" d=\"M18.5 9v18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </a>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">A：</span>\n        {% if lang == 'en' %}We will inform you of the payment method after October 14.{%- else -%}10月14日以降にご入金方法をご連絡いたします。{% endif %}\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"faq-question\">\n        <div class=\"faq-question-text\">\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">Q</span>\n          {% if lang == 'en' %}When will the product be shipped?{%- else -%}発送はいつ頃ですか？{% endif %}\n        </div>\n        <svg class=\"toggle-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 36 36\">\n          <path class=\"bar-horizontal\" d=\"M9 18.5h18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n          <path class=\"bar-vertical\" d=\"M18.5 9v18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </a>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">A：</span>\n        {% if lang == 'en' %}Shipping will begin sequentially after payment confirmation from October 14, 2025. Delivery will take 2–6 weeks after payment. In case of production delays, we will inform you in advance.{%- else -%}2025年10月14日以降での決済確認後、順次発送を致します。入金確認後2～6週間の納期となります。生産状況で遅延が生じる場合は事前に連絡いたします。{% endif %}\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"faq-question\">\n        <div class=\"faq-question-text\">\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">Q</span>\n          {% if lang == 'en' %}Can I pay by invoice?{%- else -%}請求書払いはできますか？{% endif %}\n        </div>\n        <svg class=\"toggle-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 36 36\">\n          <path class=\"bar-horizontal\" d=\"M9 18.5h18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n          <path class=\"bar-vertical\" d=\"M18.5 9v18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </a>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">A：</span>\n        {% if lang == 'en' %}Yes. After submitting the reservation form, please consult with the staff via email.{%- else -%}可能です。その場合は予約フォーム記入後にメールにてご連絡を差し上げる担当へとご相談をお願いいたします。{% endif %}\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"faq-question\">\n        <div class=\"faq-question-text\">\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">Q</span>\n          {% if lang == 'en' %}Can a receipt be issued?{%- else -%}領収書は発行されますか？{% endif %}\n        </div>\n        <svg class=\"toggle-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 36 36\">\n          <path class=\"bar-horizontal\" d=\"M9 18.5h18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n          <path class=\"bar-vertical\" d=\"M18.5 9v18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </a>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">A：</span>\n        {% if lang == 'en' %}Yes, a receipt can be issued.{%- else -%}発行可能です。{% endif %}\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"faq-question\">\n        <div class=\"faq-question-text\">\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">Q</span>\n          {% if lang == 'en' %}Are you a Qualified Invoice Issuer?{%- else -%}適格事業者ですか？{% endif %}\n        </div>\n        <svg class=\"toggle-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 36 36\">\n          <path class=\"bar-horizontal\" d=\"M9 18.5h18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n          <path class=\"bar-vertical\" d=\"M18.5 9v18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </a>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">A：</span>\n        {% if lang == 'en' %}Yes, we have obtained a Qualified Invoice Issuer Number.{%- else -%}適格事業者番号を取得しております。{% endif %}\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"faq-question\">\n        <div class=\"faq-question-text\">\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">Q</span>\n          {% if lang == 'en' %}Can I see the product in person?{%- else -%}実物をみることはできますか？{% endif %}\n        </div>\n        <svg class=\"toggle-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 36 36\">\n          <path class=\"bar-horizontal\" d=\"M9 18.5h18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n          <path class=\"bar-vertical\" d=\"M18.5 9v18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </a>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">A：</span>\n        {% if lang == 'en' %}Yes, the “Algae Stool” is exhibited at the Japan Pavilion of the 2025 Japan International Expo (Osaka/Kansai Expo). Please note that the logo mark on the seat of the stool at the venue is not included in the product for sale.{%- else -%}2025年日本国際博覧会（大阪・関西万博）の「日本政府館」にて、「藻類スツール」を展示しております。なお、会場に展示されているスツールの座面にある日本館のロゴマークは、販売品には含まれませんのでご了承ください。{% endif %}\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"contact\" id=\"contact\">\n    <h2 class=\"contact-title\">\n      {% if lang == 'en' %}Inquiries about the Product{%- else -%}製品に関する<br class=\"br-sp\">お問い合わせ相談{% endif %}\n    </h2>\n    <p>{% if lang == 'en' %}We usually reply within 3 business days.{%- else -%}通常３営業日以内に返信します。{% endif %}</p>\n    <a href=\"{% if lang == 'en' or lang == 'en-us' or lang == 'en-gb' %}/en/pages/contact{% elsif lang == 'zh' %}/zh/pages/contact{%- else -%}/pages/contact{% endif %}\">{% if lang == 'en' %}Contact Form{%- else -%}問い合わせフォーム{% endif %}</a>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n\n<style>\n.faq-title {\n  font-size: 28px;\n  margin-bottom: 24px;\n  text-align: center;\n  color: #FFF;\n}\n.faq-container {\n  margin-inline: 20rem;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  gap: 2rem;\n}\n.faq-item {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  gap: 1px;\n}\n.faq-question {\n  width: 100%;\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: center;\n  background: #FFFFFF;\n  text-decoration: none;\n  padding: 2px 0 2px 15px;\n  font-size: 14px;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  color: #8B6B3F;\n}\n.faq-question:hover {\n  opacity: 0.5;\n}\n.faq-icon {\n}\n.toggle-icon {\n  width: 36px;\n  height: 36px;\n  flex-shrink: 0;\n  display: block;\n}\n.bar-vertical {\n  transition: opacity 0.3s;\n}\n.faq-item.active .bar-vertical {\n  opacity: 0; /* 開いたときは縦棒を非表示にして－に */\n}\n.faq-answer {\n  display: none;\n  background: #fff;\n  padding: 15px;\n  font-size: 13px;\n  line-height: 1.6;\n  color: #8B6B3F;\n}\n.faq-item.active .faq-answer {\n  display: block;\n}\n.contact {\n  margin-top: 5rem;\n  text-align: center;\n}\n.contact .contact-title {\n  font-size: 28px;\n  margin-bottom: 24px;\n  text-align: center;\n  color: #FFF;\n  margin: 0 0 1rem;\n  padding: 0;\n  letter-spacing: 0.2rem;\n}\n.contact p {\n  font-size: 16px;\n  color: #FFF;\n  margin: 0;\n  padding: 0;\n  letter-spacing: 0.2rem;\n}\n.contact a {\n  display: inline-block;\n  margin-top: 1rem;\n  padding: 0px 20px;\n  font-size: 24px;\n  background-color: #FFFFFF;\n  color: #8B6B3F;\n  text-decoration: none;\n  letter-spacing: 0.2rem;\n}\n.contact a:hover {\n  opacity: 0.5;\n}\n@media screen and (max-width: 749px) {\n\t.faq-container {\n\t\tmargin-inline: 2rem;\n\t}\n}\n</style>\n\n<script>\ndocument.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function() {\n  const faqItems = document.querySelectorAll(\".faq-item\");\n  faqItems.forEach(item => {\n    item.querySelector(\".faq-question\").addEventListener(\"click\", function(e) {\n      e.preventDefault();\n      item.classList.toggle(\"active\");\n    });\n  });\n});\n</script>"
      },
      "blocks": {}
    }
  }
}
